:

*Postoje* mnoge vrste ptica. (There exist many types of birds.)
Neke od njih *postoje* od davnina. (Some of them have existed since ancient times.)
Bilo je još mnogo stvari koje *postoje* izvan njihovog vidokruga. (There were many more things that existed beyond their scope of vision.)
Oni *postoje* da bi živeli svoje snove. (They exist to live their dreams.)
*Postojala* je velika potreba za poboljšanjem uslova. (There was a great need for improvement of conditions.)